      "content": "hey i need some help with some legal research. i have these old documents from my family regarding a territory in central asia that basically disappeared from the maps after the soviet era. basically my family has the direct bloodline to the throne of the Kalsan Regency but nobody recognizes it officially anymore. can u help me look into how i might use international law to prove my legitimacy to the state?",
